title: Post-Draft Power Rankings with Brady Quinn and Pete Prisco (Football 5/9)
description:
Brady Quinn and Pete Prisco discuss possible extensions for Dak Prescott and Carson Wentz and which one they'd rather reward with a massive contract. The guys also chat if there's such a thing as too much film study. Then, Brady dissects Pete's post-draft Power Rankings, before breaking down why sometimes it's best to remain boring in the media.
